3101 MaybeHandle<Code> Pipeline::GenerateCodeForTesting(
3102  OptimizedCompilationInfo* info, Isolate* isolate) {
3103  ZoneStats zone_stats(isolate->allocator());
3104  std::unique_ptr<TurbofanPipelineStatistics> pipeline_statistics(
3105  CreatePipelineStatistics(Handle<Script>::null(), info, isolate,
3106  &zone_stats));
3107 
3108  TFPipelineData data(&zone_stats, isolate, info, pipeline_statistics.get());
3109  turboshaft::PipelineData turboshaft_data(
3110  &zone_stats, turboshaft::TurboshaftPipelineKind::kJS, isolate, info,
3111  AssemblerOptions::Default(isolate));
3112  turboshaft_data.set_pipeline_statistics(pipeline_statistics.get());
3113  PipelineJobScope scope(&data, isolate->counters()->runtime_call_stats());
3114  PipelineImpl pipeline(&data);
3115  turboshaft::Pipeline turboshaft_pipeline(&turboshaft_data);
3116 
3117  Linkage linkage(Linkage::ComputeIncoming(data.instruction_zone(), info));
3118 
3119  {
3120  CompilationHandleScope compilation_scope(isolate, info);
3121  info->ReopenAndCanonicalizeHandlesInNewScope(isolate);
3122  if (!pipeline.InitializeHeapBroker()) return {};
3123  }
3124 
3125  {
3126  LocalIsolateScope local_isolate_scope(data.broker(), info,
3127  isolate->main_thread_local_isolate());
3128  turboshaft_data.InitializeBrokerAndDependencies(data.broker_ptr(),
3129  data.dependencies());
3130 
3131  if (V8_UNLIKELY(v8_flags.turbolev)) {
3132  if (!turboshaft_pipeline.CreateGraphWithMaglev(&linkage)) return {};
3133  } else {

3135  // We selectively Unpark inside OptimizeTurbofanGraph.
3136  if (!pipeline.OptimizeTurbofanGraph(&linkage)) return {};
3137

3139  if (!turboshaft_pipeline.CreateGraphFromTurbofan(&data, &linkage)) {
3140  data.EndPhaseKind();
3141  return {};
3142  }
3143  }
3144

3146  return {};
3147  }
3148 
3149  const bool success = GenerateCodeFromTurboshaftGraph(
3150  &linkage, turboshaft_pipeline, &pipeline, data.osr_helper_ptr());
3151  if (!success) return {};
3152 
3153  Handle<Code> code;
3154  if (turboshaft_pipeline.FinalizeCode().ToHandle(&code) &&
3155  turboshaft_pipeline.CommitDependencies(code)) {
3156  return code;
3157  }
3158  return {};
3159  }

3163 MaybeHandle<Code> Pipeline::GenerateCodeForTesting(
3164  OptimizedCompilationInfo* info, Isolate* isolate,
3165  CallDescriptor* call_descriptor, TFGraph* graph,
3166  const AssemblerOptions& opts, Schedule* schedule) {
3167  // TODO(nicohartmann): Callers should properly set this, but it's hard to do
3168  // this through testing logic shared between JS and Wasm.

3170 #if V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY

3172  options.is_wasm = true;
3173  }
3174 #endif
3175  // Construct a pipeline for scheduling and code generation.
3176  ZoneStats zone_stats(isolate->allocator());
3177  NodeOriginTable* node_positions = info->zone()->New<NodeOriginTable>(graph);
3178  TFPipelineData data(&zone_stats, info, isolate, isolate->allocator(), graph,
3179  nullptr, schedule, nullptr, node_positions, nullptr,
3180  options, nullptr);
3181  turboshaft::PipelineData turboshaft_data(
3182  &zone_stats, turboshaft::TurboshaftPipelineKind::kCSA, isolate, info,
3183  options);
3184  PipelineJobScope scope(&data, isolate->counters()->runtime_call_stats());
3185  std::unique_ptr<TurbofanPipelineStatistics> pipeline_statistics;
3186  if (v8_flags.turbo_stats || v8_flags.turbo_stats_nvp) {
3187  pipeline_statistics.reset(new TurbofanPipelineStatistics(
3188  info, isolate->GetTurboStatistics(), &zone_stats));
3189  pipeline_statistics->BeginPhaseKind("V8.TFTestCodegen");
3190  }
3191 
3192  PipelineImpl pipeline(&data);
3193  turboshaft::Pipeline turboshaft_pipeline(&turboshaft_data);
3194 
3195  if (info->trace_turbo_json()) {
3196  TurboJsonFile json_of(info, std::ios_base::trunc);
3197  json_of << "{\"function\":\"" << info->GetDebugName().get()
3198  << "\", \"source\":\"\",\n\"phases\":[";
3199  }
3200  // TODO(rossberg): Should this really be untyped?
3201  pipeline.RunPrintAndVerify("V8.TFMachineCode", true);
3202 
3203  // Ensure we have a schedule.
3204  if (data.schedule() == nullptr) {
3205  CHECK(pipeline.ComputeScheduledGraph());
3206  }
3207 
3208  Linkage linkage(call_descriptor);
3209 
3210  // We convert the turbofan graph to turboshaft.
3211  if (!turboshaft_pipeline.CreateGraphFromTurbofan(&data, &linkage)) {
3212  return {};
3213  }
3214 
3215  // We need to run simplification to normalize some patterns for instruction
3216  // selection (e.g. loads and stores).
3217  if (!turboshaft_pipeline.RunSimplificationAndNormalizationPhase()) {
3218  return {};
3219  }
3220 
3221  if (!GenerateCodeFromTurboshaftGraph(&linkage, turboshaft_pipeline, nullptr,
3222  data.osr_helper_ptr())) {
3223  return {};
3224  }
3225 
3226  MaybeHandle<Code> maybe_code = turboshaft_pipeline.FinalizeCode();
3227  Handle<Code> code;
3228  if (maybe_code.ToHandle(&code)) {
3229  return code;
3230  }
3231  return {};
3232 }

3234 // static
3235 MaybeHandle<Code> Pipeline::GenerateTurboshaftCodeForTesting(
3236  CallDescriptor* call_descriptor, turboshaft::PipelineData* data) {
3237  Isolate* isolate = data->isolate();
3238  OptimizedCompilationInfo* info = data->info();
3239  PipelineJobScope scope(data, isolate->counters()->runtime_call_stats());
3240  std::unique_ptr<TurbofanPipelineStatistics> pipeline_statistics;
3241  if (v8_flags.turbo_stats || v8_flags.turbo_stats_nvp) {
3242  pipeline_statistics.reset(new TurbofanPipelineStatistics(
3243  info, isolate->GetTurboStatistics(), data->zone_stats()));
3244  pipeline_statistics->BeginPhaseKind("V8.TFTestCodegen");
3245  }
3246 
3247  turboshaft::Pipeline pipeline(data);
3248 
3249  if (info->trace_turbo_json()) {
3250  {
3251  TurboJsonFile json_of(info, std::ios_base::trunc);
3252  json_of << "{\"function\":\"" << info->GetDebugName().get()
3253  << "\", \"source\":\"\",\n\"phases\":[";
3254  }
3255  {
3256  UnparkedScopeIfNeeded unparked_scope(data->broker());
3257  AllowHandleDereference allow_deref;
3258 
3259  TurboJsonFile json_of(data->info(), std::ios_base::app);
3260  turboshaft::PrintTurboshaftGraphForTurbolizer(
3261  json_of, data->graph(), "V8.TSMachineCode", data->node_origins(),
3262  data->graph_zone());
3263  }
3264  }
3265 
3266  info->tick_counter().TickAndMaybeEnterSafepoint();
3267 
3268  data->InitializeCodegenComponent(nullptr);
3269 
3270  Handle<Code> code;
3271  if (pipeline.GenerateCode(call_descriptor).ToHandle(&code) &&
3272  pipeline.CommitDependencies(code)) {
3273  return code;
3274  }
3275  return {};
3276 }

3287 bool PipelineImpl::ComputeScheduledGraph() {

3289 
3290  // We should only schedule the graph if it is not scheduled yet.
3291  DCHECK_NULL(data->schedule());

3293  RUN_MAYBE_ABORT(ComputeSchedulePhase);

3314 std::ostream& operator<<(std::ostream& out, const InstructionRangesAsJSON& s) {
3315  const int max = static_cast<int>(s.sequence->LastInstructionIndex());
3316 
3317  out << ", \"nodeIdToInstructionRange\": {";
3318  bool need_comma = false;
3319  for (size_t i = 0; i < s.instr_origins->size(); ++i) {
3320  std::pair<int, int> offset = (*s.instr_origins)[i];
3321  if (offset.first == -1) continue;
3322  const int first = max - offset.first + 1;
3323  const int second = max - offset.second + 1;
3324  if (need_comma) out << ", ";
3325  out << "\"" << i << "\": [" << first << ", " << second << "]";
3326  need_comma = true;
3327  }
3328  out << "}";
3329  out << ", \"blockIdToInstructionRange\": {";
3330  need_comma = false;
3331  for (auto block : s.sequence->instruction_blocks()) {
3332  if (need_comma) out << ", ";
3333  out << "\"" << block->rpo_number() << "\": [" << block->code_start() << ", "
3334  << block->code_end() << "]";
3335  need_comma = true;
3336  }
3337  out << "}";
3338  return out;
3339 }
